# Explicit baseline-JSON allow-list — committed regression gates
# referenced by 00.5-VALIDATION.md (Phase 0.5 Plan 06 capacity benchmark).
# The Phase 0 _footprint-baseline.json is intentionally NOT allow-listed
# here: it is regenerated per Plan 00-06 run and historically remained
# untracked; the existing untracked file on dev machines is normal.
!tests/load/_pool-a-capacity-baseline.json

